\f2\fs18 \cf5 \super 24\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When the time came for her to give birth,\'a0there were twin boys in her womb.
\f2\b\fs18 \super 25\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The first to come out was red,\'a0and his whole body was like a hairy garment;\'a0so they named him Esau.
\fs15 \super [d]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 26\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub After this, his brother came out,\'a0with his hand grasping Esau\'92s heel;\'a0so he was named Jacob.  Gen 25\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
