\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}2 names for two different reasons\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The first is Esau and it\'92s about how he looks\'85its for many a label and an identity for us today.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They named the second one Jacob which means heal grabber and deceiver.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And for some of you there is something you did and it defines who you are just like Jacob\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf6 Transition:  So, fast forward many years and the two kids are older and the mom overhears a plan to bless the older instead of the younger\'85because dad likes the older one more than the younger and mom likes the younger instead of the older\'85it\'92s messed up.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b0 \cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your dad is trying to trick us all do something in secret that isn\'92t right.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So what\'92s the solution\'85be mature about have a conversation with the whole family?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}NOPE!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So she gets all secretive herself and starts to control her favorite son.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 8\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Now, my son, listen carefully and do what I tell you:\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 9\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Go out to the flock and bring me two choice young goats,\'a0so I can prepare some tasty food for your father, just the way he likes it.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 10\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then take it to your father to eat, so that he may give you his blessing\'a0before he dies.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He\'92s blind so he won\'92t know the difference\'85she tricking a blind guy!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}She is telling Jacob to lie and scheme to get what she and he wants for his life.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is pretty messed up right here.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The mom is scheming against one of her kids for the other kid and doing it by tricking her husband!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It doesn\'92t get much more messed up than this.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 11\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jacob said to Rebekah his mother, \'93But my brother Esau is a hairy man\'a0while I have smooth skin.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want to point out\'85his problem with the plan isn\'92t the morality of it but practicality of it\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He\'92s not worried about sinning and lying he\'92s worried about getting caught\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 12\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub What if my father touches me?\'a0I would appear to be tricking him and would bring down a curse\'a0on myself rather than a blessing.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Again, he is worried about appearing to trick his father, not that he IS tricking his father.  He\'92s worried about appearing one way while in reality he\'92s something else.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 13\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub His mother said to him, \'93My son, let the curse fall on me.\'a0Just do what I say;\'a0go and get them for me.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So much wrong here but let me point out a few things\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}1 \'96 mom tells him that she\'92ll take all the blame\'85and this works if there is no God and you\'92re 8!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}2 \'96 Jacob is roughly 80 at this moment in time and at some point you have to quit letting mom telling you what to do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you\'92re above the age of let\'92s say 18 your mom\'92s influence should be less than when you were 4!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 14\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So he went and got them and brought them to his mother, and she prepared some tasty food, just the way his father liked it.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 15\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then Rebekah took the best clothes\'a0of Esau her older son,\'a0which she had in the house, and put them on her younger son Jacob.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}She dressed him!!!!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Again\'85if you\'92re an adult and your mom is laying out what to wear for you\'85you need help!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 16\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub She also covered his hands and the smooth part of his neck with the goatskins.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 17\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then she handed to her son Jacob the tasty food and the bread she had made.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So what is happening here?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jacob wants the blessing of his father, but to get it he has to pretend to be someone he\'91s not.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And as we say all the time, their story is our story.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We do this all the time.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We pretend to be who we are not\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want the blessing or approval of someone who is important in our lives and so we pretend to be someone else.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We dress like other people to impress\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We play sports as kids to impress our parents\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We talk like others\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We take jobs we don\'92t necessarily like or want to impress others\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We lie about things to sound more impressive than we really are\'85we call it exaggerating but really it is lying.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We pretend to be cleaner, more organized, more put together than we really are\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We present to others a version of ourselves that we would like to be instead of who we really are\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We pretend on Facebook \'96 if only our lives were as great as we pretend they are on Facebook and snapchat\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When I seek the blessing of others I\'92ll miss the blessing of God\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f0\b0 \cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Who is it right now you\'92re trying to impress?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 18\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He went to his father and said, \'93My father.\'94\
\'93Yes, my son,\'94 he answered. \'93Who is it?\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Again, we talked about this last week but when someone asks who you are\'85what do you tell them?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What defines you?  Your name, your job, your income, your car, your house?  Your kids?  What?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Who do you say you are?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 19\'a0
\f0\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jacob said to his father, \'93I am Esau your firstborn.\'a0I have done as you told me. Please sit up and eat some of my game,\'a0so that you may give me your blessing.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Bless me!  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Look what I did\'85bless me!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Look who I\'92ve become\'85bless me!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 20\'a0
